research_municipality_step.notes: The list of elected officials was compiled from the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory and the official City of Lytle website. Ruben Gonzalez is identified as the Mayor. David Emery serves as the Council Member for District 3 and also holds the designation of Mayor Pro-Tem. The remaining Council Members and their respective districts are Michael Rodriguez (District 4), Miguel Aguirre (District 1), Richard Hughes (District 2), and Mathew Martinez (District 5). The official City of Lytle website confirms a Mayor and five City Council members.
